# Large media — store externally (Google Drive, S3, etc.)
Markiting videos/
Marketing/
Handoffs/
BATTLE/
Other Games/
Ad images/

# Solana Vibes Kit audit artifact dirs — these stay TRACKED (.audit/, .bok/,
# .bulwark/, .docs/) because they're the audit evidence judges read. Their
# per-run history archives are NOT tracked — they piled up at every audit
# run and cluttered the root with hundreds of stale files.
.audit-history/
.bulwark-history/
.bok-history/
.anchor/

# Local agent / planning state — never tracked. .planning/ + .claude/ were
# previously committed by accident; they're untracked now and shouldn't
# come back.
.agents/
.claude/
.planning/
.design-canvas.state.json
.mcp.json

# Old design exploration prototypes (not the live build)
/src/
/styles/
/mobile/

# Misc local artefacts
SolShot_Redesign.html
converted-repo.txt
